school days ( simplified chinese : 学校霸王 ; traditional chinese : 學校霸王 ; pinyin : xuéxiào bàwáng ) is a 1995 taiwan teen drama film distributed for hong kong . starring jimmy lin , takeshi kaneshiro and ruby lin . directed by kevin chu . the original taiwan release title of the film was " campus squad " ( 校園敢死隊 , xiàoyuán gǎnsǐduì ) , the title was renamed for its hong kong release and dubbed in cantonese to appeal to the hong kong audience .